Class DataPackageTests

  • java.lang.Object
    • DataPackageTests
  • public class DataPackageTests
extends java.lang.Object
    These are the unit tests for the data package. The classes that will be tested are Pin.java, PinFactory.java, GenericPin.java, LocationPin.java, GenericPin.java, and Admin.java. If any of these tests fail then the application will not function properly.
